data.description:
Welcome home to this spacious 3 bedroom 2 full bathroom home. Located in Shady Grove subdivision within South Bossier on a large fully fenced corner lot. Tile flooring throughout, boasting 2 living areas for a growing family, where you can step outside from your den on to a fully covered backyard patio perfect for entertaining. Desirable neighborhood with South Bossier schools and minutes from Mike Woods Park. 
It has a 4.5% ASSUMABLE FHA LOAN*Buyer must qualify to assume and give a release of liability to the current seller.
